# Transient factory runtime state — not committed. The durable, reviewable artifacts
# (PLAN.md, config, schema, _workflow code, agents, verify, setup, templates) ARE committed;
# everything below is regenerable, and — per SETUP.md — is HOST data that must never enter
# this engine repo (KI-E26: findings name real systems, and the decision queue quotes
# customer-reported detail verbatim).
state/worktrees/
state/run-args.json
state/items/
state/normalized/
# Runtime markers/leases + --fresh backups (KI-C11 / KI-E6 / setup/init.mjs)
state/controller.json
state/STOP_REQUESTED.md
state/*.pre-fresh-*
# Host-local overrides (KI-E17 / SETUP.md § 6) — per-host, never committed
config/factory.config.local.json
verify/build-test.local.sh
# Telemetry stream (KI-E7 / spine AD-8) — generated event data, never committed
telemetry/data/*
!telemetry/data/.gitkeep
# Per-host runtime artifacts (KI-E26) — the work items, the ledger, generated reports and the
# owner queue are the HOST's data, regenerated by `driver init` / `escalations` on every host.
state/ledger.json
state/findings-graph.json
state/PROGRESS.md
state/run-script*.js
state/results-*.json
reports/*
!reports/.gitkeep
queue/*
!queue/.gitkeep
